Ice spear does around 1440 with ID3.<br>
<br>
Partner .. 65 bard .. using dots.<br>
<br>
I snare mob at 98 percent .. I don't pull aggro.<br>
I concussion .. drops aggro by 400.<br>
I am on horse .. so no sit aggro.<br>
<br>
The mobs health hits 80% .. or has around 19200 hitpoints left ( Bard has done 4800 dot damage.<br>
I nuke once. 1440 damage.<br>
